{"TopicId":157315,"ForumId":25,"TopicTitle":"Make a stock hover board and ride around the KSC","CreatedByName":"TechTier","CreatedById":177899,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-04T15:12:53Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"TechTier","CreatedById":177899,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-04T15:12:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI think it would be cute to see a kerbal zipping around the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Kerbal Space Center\u0022\u003Eksc\u003C/abbr\u003E on a tiny ( or gigantic), hover board. Once you get your results, I would love to see them down below. Look forward to seeing that soon, and have fun.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003ERequirements for Challenge\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003EAllowed:\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMods, \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003Esas\u003C/abbr\u003E, kerbal has to be visible in command seat, must hover above ground,\u00A0must have video or picture of kerbal on top of \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E with hoverboard, can use jet or lift surface spinner, and you must have fun doing it!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cu\u003ENot Allowed\u003C/u\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\ncheats, wheels( this is supposed to hover), must be intact after course is finished.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cu\u003E\u003Cem\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EMission Guidelines\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/em\u003E\u003C/u\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Start on runway\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. Go through one of the R\u0026amp;D tunnels\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. Circle the mk1 memorial in the center\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. Go to the launching pad\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5. Align on top of pad\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n6. Hover up into the air until over \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n7. Land on \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E helipad\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n8. Plant flag\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n9. Land on edge of runway where you started.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n10. Have fun! \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"vat21s","CreatedById":34187,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-05T06:25:09Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/BoJwdO4mujY?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-12T08:05:22Z\u0022 title=\u002203/12/2017 08:05  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 12, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by vat21s\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EEntry Completed\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"blaw","CreatedById":175621,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-07T13:17:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhen it will be publish.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Numerlor","CreatedById":174198,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-08T14:40:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you try it? I\u0027m trying to build something that could do this but it simply isn\u0027t possible for me because throttle is hardly controllable because of fuel consumption and breaking with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E isn\u0027t that easy too\u003Cbr\u003E\nand I won\u0027t even start on landing\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-08T14:40:20Z\u0022 title=\u002203/08/2017 02:40  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 8, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Numerlor\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-08T19:24:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nperhaps make it a requirement to use that mod (cant remember the name \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E) that lets you fine tune your thrust to let things hover?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Jollyfellow","CreatedById":162854,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-03-19T03:32:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust made a hovercraft and completed the challenge. Unfortunately due to the fact that I don\u0027t know how to use OBS hardly at all, it\u0027s poor-ish\u00A0quality without sound...\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/rRtzpVL3_Jc\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttps://youtu.be/rRtzpVL3_Jc\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n(Also, if someone could tell me how to embed this video, it\u0027d be appreciated, thank you!)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-03-19T03:58:33Z\u0022 title=\u002203/19/2017 03:58  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EMarch 19, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Jollyfellow\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vinhero100","CreatedById":170677,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-04T21:35:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222979881\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221489001051\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166190\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022nascarlaser1\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/8/2017 at 2:24 PM, nascarlaser1 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nperhaps make it a requirement to use that mod (cant remember the name \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E) that lets you fine tune your thrust to let things hover?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIm pretty sure you mean Throttle Control Systems (I think that\u0027s the name)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"nascarlaser1","CreatedById":166190,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-04T21:46:21Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223009659\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221491341716\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022170677\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Vinhero100\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 minutes ago, Vinhero100 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIm pretty sure you mean Throttle Control Systems (I think that\u0027s the name)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyup thxs!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vinhero100","CreatedById":170677,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-04T21:59:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve got a prototype, completely stock:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther ipsEmbeddedOther_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=http://imgur.com/a/r2kbR\u0022 style=\u0022height:454px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-04T22:24:07Z\u0022 title=\u002204/04/2017 10:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Vinhero100\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KenjiKrafts","CreatedById":175750,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-04T22:18:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222979564\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022157315\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221488984008\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022174198\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Numerlor\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 3/8/2017 at 2:40 PM, Numerlor said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDid you try it? I\u0027m trying to build something that could do this but it simply isn\u0027t possible for me because throttle is hardly controllable because of fuel consumption and breaking with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E isn\u0027t that easy too\u003Cbr\u003E\nand I won\u0027t even start on landing\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nUse a more efficient engine, failing that use mono prop engines, failing that make a \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vertical Take-Off and Landing\u0022\u003EVTOL\u003C/abbr\u003E glider, for landing use Large Landing Legs \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI am joining btw \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:cool:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cool.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:cool:\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-04T22:19:00Z\u0022 title=\u002204/04/2017 10:19  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by KenjiKrafts\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EI am joining btw\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vinhero100","CreatedById":170677,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-04T22:37:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne question: At any part of the flight, can this touch the ground?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Vinhero100","CreatedById":170677,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-04T23:38:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedOther ipsEmbeddedOther_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?app=core\u0026amp;module=system\u0026amp;controller=embed\u0026amp;url=http://imgur.com/a/BcFYd\u0022 style=\u0022height:435px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nP.S.- My 100th post!!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-04-04T23:39:30Z\u0022 title=\u002204/04/2017 11:39  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EApril 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Vinhero100\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Triop","CreatedById":145841,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-04-05T00:22:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n1. Start on runway\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n2. \u003Cs\u003EGo through one of the R\u0026amp;D tunnels\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n3. \u003Cs\u003ECircle the mk1 memorial in the center\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n4. \u003Cs\u003EGo to the launching pad\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n5. \u003Cs\u003EAlign on top of pad\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n6. \u003Cs\u003EHover up into the air until over \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n7. \u003Cs\u003ELand on \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Vehicle Assembly Building\u0022\u003EVAB\u003C/abbr\u003E helipad\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n8. \u003Cs\u003EPlant flag\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n9. \u003Cs\u003ELand on edge of runway where you started.\u003C/s\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n10. Have fun! \u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThis would have tickled me...\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}